---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Container } from "@/components/layout/Container";
import HeroImage from "../components/ui/HeroImage.astro";
import { ArrowRight } from "lucide-react";
---

<Layout
    title="Starting a Daycare at Home | Childcare Business Plan"
    description="Your home-based daycare opportunity depends on your state's regulations, zoning laws, and local market. Get personalized insights for your situation."
>
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <HeroImage
                src="/images/startup/starting-a-daycare-at-home.webp"
                alt="Home office setup with licensing documents, essential for the starting a daycare center checklist phase"
                className="mb-4 md:mb-12"
            />
            <div class="text-center">
                <span class="pro-text-meta mb-2 block">
                    Home-Based Business
                </span>
                <h1 class="text-xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6">
                    YOUR Home-Based Daycare
                </h1>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                    Running a daycare from home offers flexibility and lower startup costs, but your actual opportunity depends entirely on your state's family childcare regulations.
                </p>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- FACTORS SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section bg-gray-50/50">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card mb-3 md:mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">
                    What Affects Your Home Daycare
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    <p>
                        Home-based daycares operate under family childcare licensing, which varies dramatically by state. Some allow up to 12 children with an assistant, while others cap you at 3. This directly sets your income ceiling.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Your home's zoning classification matters too. Residential zoning might restrict operations, require special permits, or limit the number of non-family members allowed.
                    </p>
                    <p class="hidden md:block">
                        Beyond regulations, your layouts, outdoor space, and proximity to families affect viability. The work-life boundaries you maintain create a unique business equation.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- WHY GENERIC FAILS SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">
                    Why Advice Conflicts
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    <p>
                        A home daycare that thrives in one state might be financially impossible in another due to capacity rules. A profitable model in a suburb might fail in a rural community.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        You can't evaluate your opportunity using someone else's numbers. Your state's regulations, local market rates, and home's suitability require personalized analysis.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card text-center border-2 border-teal-200/50 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50/20 to-white/50">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-4">
                    See Real Home Daycare Potential
                </h2>
                <p class="text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 mb-3 md:mb-6">
                    Get your personalized income estimate based on your state's family childcare regulations.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="/#calculator"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-bold px-5 py-2 md:px-8 md:py-4 shadow-lg transition-all text-xs md:text-base group"
                >
                    Use the Free Calculator
                    <ArrowRight className="w-3.5 h-3.5 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" />
                </a>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>
</Layout>
